Package: propMetaTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Proportional Meta Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Abu Suraih Sakhri
Maintainer: Abu Suraih Sakhri<abusuraihsakhri@gmail.com>
Description: propMetaTools is an R package designed to simplify
    proportional meta analysis workflows used in epidemiology
    and clinical research. The package provides tools for
    preparing datasets, performing meta analysis using
    Freeman-Tukey transformation, and evaluating publication
    bias through funnel plot diagnostics and regression tests.
